{"tid":717691,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"超霸鷹教頭：對美斯決不手下留情！","createTime":"2018-06-26T08:32:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-26T09:18:49.000Z","uid":46892,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"c5143e8e07e6f3ffbba4657187f911c4d0d7b1cc","tid":717691,"uid":46892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T08:32:50.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=AUEgvheeUj78fjgBelS1%2Fozu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=f50b8df4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】世界盃D組尼日利亞對阿根廷，賽前人人都以「美斯世盃絕唱」作話題之際，尼軍教頭羅亞揚言絕對不會手下留情。<br />\n<br />\n「我們都很愛美斯，但絕不會手下留情。我們來俄羅斯並非為了看美斯表演，我們來這裡是為了競技，為了爭勝。我們一心打入16強，絕不會讓美斯與他的阿根廷踩著我們的頭過關。」超霸鷹的教頭羅亞（Gernot Rohr）斬釘截鐵的說。<br />\n<br />\n今場將會是尼軍歷來在世盃第6次面對阿根廷，論名氣雖然輸蝕，但羅亞說：「阿根廷的世界排名在頭10位，我們第48位，但這一點無關痛癢。我們對16強一席是如饑似渴。」<br />\n<br />\n雖然不願事先張揚陣式，但羅亞強調今場不會再輕率犯錯，「今場必定精彩。我們可以踢4-3-2-1或者4-4-2甚至3-5-2，我只能說今場肯定不會像頭兩場（對克羅地亞和冰島）那樣大意，被判罰兩球無謂的12碼。我們在防守方面落力訓練，確保今場對阿根廷不會再犯下同類的愚蠢錯誤。」"},{"pid":"09298fba98aa87159e8f75105fc691c1b70703de","tid":717691,"uid":18569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T08:48:53.000Z","msg":"小花會唔會腳仔軟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42e045139bb1d49c6a9ac50b0fd904a5f6fbaefe","tid":717691,"uid":111253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T08:53:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/nigeria.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/nigeria.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/nigeria.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/nigeria.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/nigeria.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/nigeria.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/nigeria.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/nigeria.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d883595b85c2dccbbb0f0e3b2fe75e9e053f968","tid":717691,"uid":65298,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T08:57:47.000Z","msg":"如饑似渴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n佢中文幾勁"},{"pid":"ffbf13ed003f889978d97bd747e05bc936b108cc","tid":717691,"uid":20449,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T09:18:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}